content: {"name": "St. Francis Episcopal Parish Community Center, Food Pantry", "alternate_name": "", "description": "FOOD PANTRY: Offers Pantry on the Go and the Indoor Choice Pantry. Pantry on the Go provides a drive-through, contact-less food distribution program offering groceries to those in need, every first Thursday of the month, beginning at 3:30PM. May begin distribution as early at 3PM if the line is substantial. The distribution ends when the food runs out. Also offers assistance through the Indoor Choice Pantry, where there are shelves of pantry items available as needed. Schedule an appointment on the website. Open Sunday, 12Noon-2PM or Wednesday evening 5PM-7PM. There is also a community garden with produce available in the summer and fall.SOUP KITCHEN: Offers a Welcome Table on Wednesdays during the school year.
